{"tid":261304,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"巨 乳 模 特 兒 自 爆 曾 短 暫 失 明","createTime":"2017-05-28T10:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T11:11:18.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5855652f448145814999acb76e26cf656ad37231","tid":261304,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T10:54:36.000Z","msg":"莊思敏、譚凱琪（Zoie）、黃美棋、黃芷晴等以性感造型出席夜店活動，大玩Beer Pong遊戲，其中以超低胸現身的莊思敏晒C奶，最有「大C姐」風範，胸壓全場！她自認酒量差：「唔飲得都要玩得，這樣才能避免因輸Game而被罰飲酒。」她又自爆曾因飲了疑似假酒而短暫失明數分鐘：「只飲了半杯紅酒便看不到東西，現場冇人信我，嚇死我呢，幸好數分鐘後便看得見，醫生說是酒精敏感，近期再飲酒也沒事。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170523/_2017052322161667661.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170523%2F_2017052322161667661.jpg&h=8d15542c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"215f09e032d1de095e7d888158076ef9f49aa755","tid":261304,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T10:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb6276728001a5e42c06b8ef4da5083371e57e7","tid":261304,"uid":50602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:11:18.000Z","msg":"假嘅&hellip;&hellip;Ｄ奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!?"}]}